description:
Join us as we go on a journey back to the source that sparked the entire world with a light that none of us can afford to die.

Could the dark ages ever return? What actually happened 500 years ago? Is this protest over? Why should you care? There are at least Ninety-Five reasons why you should....

To find out more information about Martin Luther read our extended article. 
http://www.lineagejourney.com/reformation/reformers/martin-luther-point-man-reformation/
